  "text": "Binding to CEA-expressing LS174T cells and IL-2-stimulated T cells from peripheral blood mononuclear cells (PBMCs) was determined by flow cytometry [CITATION_1] . 2.5 x 10 5 cells were incubated with dilution series of antibodies for 2 h at 4°C. Cells were then washed with PBS, 2% FBS, 0.02% NaN 3 (PBA) and bound antibodies were detected with PE-conjugated mouse antiHis-tag antibody.",
